<a Title="Profit Margin of Sales:
This percentage represents the percent of your revenues 
that is Net Income.For example if you have a Profit 
Margin of Sales of 10% this means you make 10 cents in 
profit for every dollar of revenues."> <img height="25" width="25" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/af/Question_mark.png" /></a>

