<a Title="Return on Assets:
This percentage represents the percent of your assets 
that is Net Income.For example if you have a Return
on Assets of 10% this means you make 10 cents in 
profit for every dollar of assets."> <img height="25" width="25" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/af/Question_mark.png" /></a>

